{"tid":536656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視第二】海航賣西班牙酒店還債 系內A股跌停牌","createTime":"2018-01-22T04:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T07:37:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b6fd8bbee4254f24ebf5e4112c8c6976c69f43","tid":536656,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180122/large/1516592504_8298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180122%2Flarge%2F1516592504_8298.jpg&h=38ff6f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《彭博》報道指，海航集團開始為其有的西班牙酒店集團NH Hotel group的30%股權尋找買家接手，估值約6.3億歐元。惟海航系多隻A股均跌停牌。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙監管當局申報指，海航已找摩通、Benedetto及Gartland&amp;Co評估其持有NH Hotel的三成股權。海航13年投資NH後，NH成功在兩年後扭虧為盈。<br />\n海航3間A股跌停牌，分別為海航創新（SH600555）、海越股份（SH600387）及海航基础（SH600515）。海航投資（SZ000616）、東北電氣（SZ000585）齊跌3%。"},{"pid":"3668e02042200350f37d147ee692ea959f8b46ad","tid":536656,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"係咪就係佢當年想拆人間酒店，俾西班牙人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017342d778213966d59ecbd5ccbc6798d782dbc8","tid":536656,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46adb2c91e7de45375b50013633f371bd65bbbaa","tid":536656,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3668e02042200350f37d147ee692ea959f8b46ad","tid":536656,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"係咪就係佢當年想拆人間酒店，俾西班牙人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"果單係萬達 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6377fa5c1f1b3fc09a5eb4fa57cce8e302ffcc1e","tid":536656,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【海航動向】海航系Ａ股集體大跌，海越股份、海航基礎跌停</span><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社２２日專訊》在滬深上市的海航系股份集體大跌，海越股份<br />\n（滬：６００３８７）及海航基礎（滬：６００５１５）開市約一小時後跌停，而海航創新（滬<br />\n：６００５５５）則挫９％，海航投資（深：０００６１６）挫３％。<br />\n<br />\n　　海航系五間Ａ股子公司上星期均以籌劃重大事項而相繼停牌，包括凱撒旅遊<br />\n<br />\n（深：０００７９６），供銷大集（深：０００５６４）、渤海金控（深：０００４１５）、海<br />\n航控股（滬：６００２２１）及天海投資（滬：６００７５１）。<br />\n<br />\n　　外電早前報道指，在海航集團提供充分的股東信息前，美國政府不會批准該公司的任何投資<br />\n。而海航集團２０１９年及２０２０年到期的債券跌至接近歷史低位。集團董事局主席陳峰承認<br />\n公司出現流動性困難，但對解決現金短缺問題感到樂觀，並稱今年將繼續獲得銀行及其他金融機<br />\n構的支持。<br />\n<br />\n　　海航系的港股表現分化，海航科技投資（０２０８６）挫３％，ＣＷＴ（００５２１）沒升<br />\n跌，香港國際建投（００６８７）將發行不少於５０００萬美元的可換股債券，大升８％。<br />\n（ｋｌ）"},{"pid":"f738575dfb7b9ff023bb71e52b778240da25eadc","tid":536656,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"新地借比佢D錢, 似乎凍過水"},{"pid":"a24c994d49bdf940aa580955a923ce1f1bb78a76","tid":536656,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f738575dfb7b9ff023bb71e52b778240da25eadc","tid":536656,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"新地借比佢D錢, 似乎凍過水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bc0378fb38296a2ac1faf424c7d5849f781afa","tid":536656,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"根本係攞正牌走資<br />\n用$12買值$10嘅嘢再$8賣走<br />\n<br />\n匯錢出咗去買嘢。賣返錢你估佢抬幾多返大陸？"},{"pid":"4fe744ff0ae3eb27e9ffde49b62e673d185b36bf","tid":536656,"uid":128014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f738575dfb7b9ff023bb71e52b778240da25eadc","tid":536656,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"新地借比佢D錢, 似乎凍過水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"新地會唔會志在想拎佢啟德塊地咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji